{"word":"G5231 - ὑπεράνω - hyperánō - hoop-er-an'-o - Far above","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπεράνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyperánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-an'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Far above</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மேலாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"above"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G507 - ἄνω - ánō - an'-o/507\">G507</a>; <i>above upward</i>, that is, <i>greatly higher</i> (in place or rank): - far above, over.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}